      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLDSTAR KLEIN (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (26.10) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Hard to knock his form from this box, unbeaten in three starts. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. SATIN SPARKLE (8) did a good job to finish third last time out over 411m at Casino (24.39) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. Can find the frame this time. NO MORE BEER (3) has a strong record here with eight wins and six placings from 17 starts. In the money last time at Q Straight (19.22) in a OPEN, finishing a 4 length third. Looks suited here and can measure up. JALAPENO POPPER (2) showed good early speed and won last start. That form reads well.",
